): preview_available=false, requires_approval=false, runtime_executable=false, decision=deny\n- Edit file (`op.edit_file`): preview_available=false, requires_approval=false, runtime_executable=false, decision=deny\n- Shell (`op.shell`): preview_available=false, requires_approval=false, runtime_executable=false, decision=deny\n- Python REPL (`op.python_repl`): preview_available=false, requires_approval=false, runtime_executable=false, decision=deny\n- Memory write candidate (`op.memory_write_candidate`): preview_available=false, requires_approval=false, runtime_executable=false, decision=deny\nProjection must not grant permissions; authorization_owner=ResourcePolicy.", "chars": 1064}, {"section_id": "projection_section", "title": "投影姿态", "source_type": "projection_requirement", "source_id": "turn:162c6a0d3d854b05ab45d36172d67b4d:3", "owner_layer": "projection", "cache_scope": "dynamic", "visible_to_model": true, "content": "Projection role: analyst. Posture tags: concise.", "chars": 48}, {"section_id": "output_section", "title": "输出边界", "source_type": "task_contract", "source_id": "turn:162c6a0d3d854b05ab45d36172d67b4d:3", "owner_layer": "task", "cache_scope": "dynamic", "visible_to_model": true, "content": "Output should satisfy task modes: request_intake. Return a concise preview-ready response.", "chars": 90}, {"section_id": "guardrail_section", "title": "护栏", "source_type": "task_binding", "source_id": "binding:task.request_intake:builtin", "owner_layer": "task", "cache_scope": "dynamic", "visible_to_model": true, "content": "Do not execute tools, workers, file writes, shell commands, or memory writes in preview.\nDo not treat ResourceRuntimeView.authorized as runtime_executable.\nReview policy: optional.", "chars": 180}], "visible_skill_ids": [], "visible_tool_ids": ["op.model_response"], "authorization_owner": "ResourcePolicy", "trace": {"projection_owner": "SoulProjectionPreview", "authorization_owner": "ResourcePolicy", "runtime_executable": "false", "preview